snippet.title: Auto RiskRisk - 2nd gameplay trailer | August 30, 2023
snippet.description:
Second public gameplay video of the autobattler Auto RiskRisk developed by Parrexion Games.

This showcases the main gameloop together with the basic actions you will perform when building your teams and then fighting the opponents.

Wishlist the game on Steam now!
